title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Disturbed and undisturbed Sampling; Standard Penetration test; Static Cone Penetration test; Plate Bearing test; In-situ Dynamic properties; Model Footing test; Model Pile Loading test; Laboratory Vibration test; Unconfined Compression test on rock specimens; Data Processing; Logging and making Report.
